1
00:00:00,950 --> 00:00:03,950
Hey, all you viewers out there!

2
00:00:03,950 --> 00:00:07,120
When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make 
sure to keep the room nice and bright,

3
00:00:07,120 --> 00:00:09,490
and sit back from the screen, 'kay?

4
00:00:10,280 --> 00:00:12,820
Previous on Fairy Tail:

5
00:00:12,820 --> 00:00:16,030
Laxus started the Battle of Fairy Tail.

6
00:00:16,030 --> 00:00:17,990
Erza defeated Eve of the Raijin Tribe,

7
00:00:17,990 --> 00:00:21,480
and those of us who were stoned 
finally turned back to normal!

8
00:00:21,480 --> 00:00:24,540
But just when we thought the game was 
over, Laxus activated the Thunder Palace,

9
00:00:24,540 --> 00:00:26,920
and everyone in the entire 
city is being held hostage!

10
00:00:26,920 --> 00:00:29,090
The real battle starts now!

11
00:00:47,560 --> 00:00:52,370
Yo Ho! Steer that rudder! Hard to port!

12
00:00:52,370 --> 00:00:55,920
Yo Ho! Our high-flyin' lives are every which way!

13
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:08,610
When the sun goes down, there's a bon voyage bash.

14
00:01:09,830 --> 00:01:14,150
It ain't sad at all.

15
00:01:14,150 --> 00:01:21,350
As long as we're alive, we'll meet again somewhere!

16
00:01:21,350 --> 00:01:25,640
Blast straight through a headwind, set off!

17
00:01:25,640 --> 00:01:30,440
Stay strong until the tears dry up! A man gotta be tough.

18
00:01:30,440 --> 00:01:35,150
Friends, friends, laugh one day!

19
00:01:35,150 --> 00:01:39,870
As proof of our strong, strong bonds!

20
00:01:39,870 --> 00:01:47,770
Now, grab that map to the shining future!

21
00:02:08,220 --> 00:02:09,390
Wow!

22
00:02:09,390 --> 00:02:11,230
It's the Lion clad in Light!

23
00:02:11,480 --> 00:02:15,530
I told you, it's no use! Your 
attacks won't affect souls!

24
00:02:15,530 --> 00:02:19,150
Because no matter how many you destroy, 
I can just manipulate other bodies!

25
00:02:19,150 --> 00:02:22,340
Get to it, my new babies!

26
00:02:27,110 --> 00:02:29,960
No matter how many come at us, 
I won't let them get near Lucy!

27
00:02:30,210 --> 00:02:31,080
Now's our chance!

28
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:32,430
Aye, sir!

29
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:35,240
Whoa there...

30
00:02:36,620 --> 00:02:38,820
Don't freak me out like 
that, cosplay princess!

31
00:02:38,820 --> 00:02:40,260
That's not it, jeez!

32
00:02:40,510 --> 00:02:42,680
Lucy, force him back!

33
00:02:42,930 --> 00:02:45,530
Bickslow himself isn't that strong!

34
00:02:45,530 --> 00:02:47,420
What the hell are you saying, you bastard!

35
00:02:48,830 --> 00:02:50,040
Damn it...

36
00:02:50,040 --> 00:02:51,810
Guess I have no choice.

37
00:02:51,810 --> 00:02:52,720
Huh?

38
00:02:52,720 --> 00:02:53,770
Could he be...

39
00:03:00,790 --> 00:03:02,680
Satan's Descent!

40
00:03:04,620 --> 00:03:06,590
Figure Eyes!

41
00:03:07,600 --> 00:03:09,590
Don't look into his eyes!

42
00:03:09,790 --> 00:03:14,300
All the Raijin Tribe have 
secondary magic in their eyes!

43
00:03:14,300 --> 00:03:16,340
Eve uses it as her main magic,

44
00:03:16,580 --> 00:03:21,090
but if you look into Bickslow's eyes, you turn 
into a doll, and your soul will be manipulated!

45
00:03:21,340 --> 00:03:22,600
Seriously?

46
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:23,760
Close call!

47
00:03:23,760 --> 00:03:25,470
So, your eyes closed?

48
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:27,350
Yup!

49
00:03:30,480 --> 00:03:33,580
Don't open your eyes, you two!

50
00:03:34,900 --> 00:03:40,070
My Doll Possession and Figure Eyes 
are an unbeatable combination!

51
00:03:40,320 --> 00:03:45,160
Lucy, close my gate temporarily 
and take shelter in Horologium!

52
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:47,320
You're the one who just showed up!

53
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:49,560
And I had my keys taken away from me!

54
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:51,000
Plus...

55
00:03:51,460 --> 00:03:54,880
I trust you, so do something!

56
00:03:57,040 --> 00:03:57,590
Right!

57
00:03:58,250 --> 00:04:00,010
Let's go for it, Lucy!

58
00:04:00,010 --> 00:04:02,430
When I give the signal, open 
your eyes and charge in!

59
00:04:02,430 --> 00:04:04,430
But if I open my eyes...

60
00:04:05,540 --> 00:04:07,650
You trust me, right?

61
00:04:07,650 --> 00:04:09,180
Got it...

62
00:04:11,310 --> 00:04:13,100
Regulus is fully risen.

63
00:04:13,430 --> 00:04:14,640
Lion Flare!

64
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:19,100
My... My eyes!

65
00:04:19,100 --> 00:04:20,040
Lucy!

66
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:20,650
Okay!

67
00:04:22,400 --> 00:04:26,060
Loke... There's no way you can beat me!

68
00:04:26,740 --> 00:04:29,120
I'm nothing like I was back then.

69
00:04:29,840 --> 00:04:34,150
I met Lucy, and I regained 
my true powers as a Spirit.

70
00:04:34,810 --> 00:04:39,120
No... I met Lucy and got even stronger!

71
00:04:39,650 --> 00:04:42,280
I'm not like those dolls you manipulate!

72
00:04:42,280 --> 00:04:44,480
Love makes Spirits stronger!

73
00:04:46,500 --> 00:04:48,840
Regulus Impact!

74
00:05:03,020 --> 00:05:04,840
Thank you, Loke.

75
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:06,290
Look, Lucy...

76
00:05:08,320 --> 00:05:10,120
The light of love!

77
00:05:10,710 --> 00:05:12,210
Uh...

78
00:05:12,210 --> 00:05:13,950
He lllllikes you...

79
00:05:13,950 --> 00:05:16,340
Please don't roll your tongue like that.

80
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:19,960
Huh? I feel so weak...

81
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:23,000
That's because you opened 
two of the Zodiac gates...

82
00:05:24,230 --> 00:05:26,550
I'll come to save you any time.

83
00:05:26,550 --> 00:05:28,710
Yeah... Thanks.

84
00:05:30,710 --> 00:05:32,130
Lucy won!

85
00:05:32,130 --> 00:05:33,230
No way!

86
00:05:33,230 --> 00:05:35,490
That cheerleader can fight?

87
00:05:35,490 --> 00:05:37,100
Lucy's strong, man.

88
00:05:37,100 --> 00:05:39,230
You're joking! I mean, she's a cheerleader!

89
00:05:39,230 --> 00:05:41,020
I knew Lu-chan could do it!

90
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:41,020
Cheerleaders <i>are</i> strong!

91
00:05:41,020 --> 00:05:42,530
I've gotta solve this, too!

92
00:05:41,020 --> 00:05:43,020
I ain't never heard that before!

93
00:05:43,270 --> 00:05:44,310
Why, you...

94
00:05:44,310 --> 00:05:47,040
Haven't you ever heard of the 
Tortoise and the Cheerleader?

95
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,750
That's a hare, not a cheer!

96
00:05:48,750 --> 00:05:50,620
And the hare lost!

97
00:05:50,870 --> 00:05:52,460
Sure, the first time.

98
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:53,340
If I can just figure this part out...

99
00:05:52,460 --> 00:05:56,110
But then the hare won like a 
hundred times in a row afterwards.

100
00:05:53,890 --> 00:05:57,000
If I rewrite the runes...

101
00:05:57,010 --> 00:05:58,970
But this is the hardest part to...

102
00:05:57,010 --> 00:06:00,170
That makes sense. Learning from failure.

103
00:06:00,670 --> 00:06:01,940
That's it!

104
00:06:01,940 --> 00:06:03,090
What's it?

105
00:06:03,090 --> 00:06:07,220
I got it! You read the two grammars 
at different rates to decipher it!

106
00:06:07,780 --> 00:06:12,470
Then I match the corresponding time differentiated
letters and convert to Gheel grammar...

107
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:14,610
Then translate into Rogue...

108
00:06:16,770 --> 00:06:18,230
I solved it!

109
00:06:20,150 --> 00:06:23,100
Wait a sec! I'll rewrite the runes!

110
00:06:23,100 --> 00:06:23,900
Yeah!

111
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:26,690
Natsu... Gajeel...

112
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:31,030
Are you ready? You're about to 
join the Battle of Fairy Tail!

113
00:06:32,900 --> 00:06:34,580
I'm all fired up!

114
00:06:34,580 --> 00:06:36,750
It's time for rampage!

115
00:06:45,390 --> 00:06:46,570
Elfman...

116
00:06:48,070 --> 00:06:49,220
Nee-chan...

117
00:06:49,820 --> 00:06:51,420
You're injured really bad...

118
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:55,260
Thank goodness... You're back to normal.

119
00:06:55,950 --> 00:06:57,470
I'm sorry, Elfman.

120
00:06:58,180 --> 00:06:59,170
I'm sorry...

121
00:06:59,870 --> 00:07:02,160
Why are you apologizing?

122
00:07:03,810 --> 00:07:08,940
Both during Phantom's attack and now...

123
00:07:10,070 --> 00:07:11,700
I wasn't able to do anything...

124
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,750
And...

125
00:07:14,670 --> 00:07:17,790
You don't have to.

126
00:07:18,200 --> 00:07:21,630
All you need to do is greet 
everyone with a smile

127
00:07:21,630 --> 00:07:24,350
after this pointless fighting is over with.

128
00:07:34,330 --> 00:07:36,080
Please...

129
00:07:37,110 --> 00:07:38,410
Don't cry.

130
00:07:41,500 --> 00:07:42,890
Juvia...

131
00:07:42,890 --> 00:07:45,680
How much longer until the 
Thunder Palace activates?

132
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:47,870
About 30 minutes, perhaps.

133
00:07:47,870 --> 00:07:49,450
Laxus, damn him...

134
00:07:49,450 --> 00:07:51,440
Battle of Fairy Tail, my ass!

135
00:07:51,690 --> 00:07:54,430
He's just hiding himself and doing nothing!

136
00:07:54,910 --> 00:07:56,630
Where can he be?

137
00:07:57,590 --> 00:07:59,900
Laxus is saving his magical power.

138
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:06,670
He's saving his energy in case he 
has to fight the master for real.

139
00:08:06,670 --> 00:08:08,200
Freed!

140
00:08:08,200 --> 00:08:10,150
So that's the person who made the runes?

141
00:08:11,020 --> 00:08:12,260
Running away?

142
00:08:15,660 --> 00:08:17,220
Wait, Freed!

143
00:08:20,850 --> 00:08:23,310
Shoot, runes!

144
00:08:23,310 --> 00:08:24,290
A trap?

145
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:29,050
Rule: Exiting these runes is forbidden,

146
00:08:29,050 --> 00:08:32,070
until one of you can no longer fight.

147
00:08:32,580 --> 00:08:34,870
I'll fight whoever the victor is.

148
00:08:34,870 --> 00:08:36,250
Now, begin.

149
00:08:36,250 --> 00:08:37,770
That's a cheap trick, Freed!

150
00:08:37,770 --> 00:08:41,630
If you wanna go at it, you don't 
have to do this! I'll take you on!

151
00:08:41,630 --> 00:08:43,720
Now let me out!

152
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:48,210
Or could it be that you're scared 
of taking us both on by yourself?

153
00:08:48,210 --> 00:08:51,970
Scared of two women? How pitiful, Freed!

154
00:08:53,510 --> 00:08:57,300
I just don't want to dirty my 
own hands if I can help it.

155
00:08:57,550 --> 00:08:59,130
Say that again, you bastard!

156
00:08:59,500 --> 00:09:02,330
So this is how you got the 
allies to fight each other...

157
00:09:02,330 --> 00:09:03,460
Allies?

158
00:09:03,910 --> 00:09:07,140
Well, I'd prefer it if Cana remained.

159
00:09:08,340 --> 00:09:09,650
Juvia Lockser...

160
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:13,030
You are and will always 
be Phantom's woman...

161
00:09:13,580 --> 00:09:18,590
Who knows when she'll turn her 
sword against Fairy Tail again?

162
00:09:18,590 --> 00:09:20,200
Damn you, Freed!

163
00:09:21,090 --> 00:09:23,930
I suppose there is nothing else to be done.

164
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:27,660
Juvia, you're...

165
00:09:28,010 --> 00:09:33,470
Freed-san, will you really fight 
the one that remains with honor?

166
00:09:33,890 --> 00:09:36,760
I will never break my rules.

167
00:09:37,680 --> 00:09:38,680
That's good to hear.

168
00:09:38,950 --> 00:09:40,570
Are you serious, Juvia?

169
00:09:40,570 --> 00:09:42,720
You'll just be playing into his...

170
00:09:46,430 --> 00:09:51,500
It's no use! You can't get out of 
the runes no matter how high you go!

171
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:56,250
If it takes being injured to open the path...

172
00:09:56,250 --> 00:09:58,400
If it's between my friend or myself...

173
00:09:59,450 --> 00:10:00,670
The lacrima?

174
00:10:00,670 --> 00:10:02,680
Don't attack that!

175
00:10:02,680 --> 00:10:04,700
Then Juvia will lead the way!

176
00:10:09,100 --> 00:10:10,440
Juvia!

177
00:10:22,310 --> 00:10:23,260
Juvia!

178
00:10:26,670 --> 00:10:30,970
This way the runes are... unlocked...

179
00:10:30,970 --> 00:10:33,350
What the hell were you thinking?

180
00:10:33,710 --> 00:10:37,820
Juvia wants people to hurry and accept her...

181
00:10:39,100 --> 00:10:42,740
...as a member of Fairy Tail...

182
00:10:43,650 --> 00:10:45,790
I love everyone...

183
00:10:46,580 --> 00:10:48,280
What are you saying?

184
00:10:48,670 --> 00:10:50,680
You're already one of us...

185
00:10:51,340 --> 00:10:55,080
Being accepted? You're already our friend...

186
00:10:55,750 --> 00:10:59,810
You're a wonderful Fairy Tail wizard!

187
00:11:00,140 --> 00:11:01,500
Cana-san...

188
00:11:02,300 --> 00:11:05,350
That makes Juvia... happy...

189
00:11:05,610 --> 00:11:07,720
Juvia!

190
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:11,370
I can't believe her...

191
00:11:11,790 --> 00:11:16,430
Instead of surviving herself, she 
chose to let her comrade live on...

192
00:11:19,860 --> 00:11:22,360
Freed!

193
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:28,190
Damn it, there's too many people.

194
00:11:28,660 --> 00:11:31,000
I can't find Laxus's smell.

195
00:11:31,730 --> 00:11:34,260
Listen up Natsu, Gajeel...

196
00:11:34,260 --> 00:11:38,040
If you get caught in Freed's runes, 
this will all be for nothing.

197
00:11:38,040 --> 00:11:41,280
When you leave here, split up, got it?

198
00:11:42,760 --> 00:11:46,490
One of these days I'll get 
my revenge on Salamander,

199
00:11:46,490 --> 00:11:49,870
but first, I'll crush that 
arrogant thunder blow hard.

200
00:11:49,870 --> 00:11:52,230
I've got quite a bone to pick with him.

201
00:11:52,580 --> 00:11:55,500
Got a problem with that, Master Ivan?

202
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:58,060
Gajeel...

203
00:11:58,730 --> 00:12:02,520
Right now, earning their 
trust is most important.

204
00:12:03,560 --> 00:12:05,640
Don't get found out.

205
00:12:06,550 --> 00:12:10,940
Act completely as a member of 
Fairy Tail, no matter what.

206
00:12:11,700 --> 00:12:14,440
I'm already doin' that.

207
00:12:14,820 --> 00:12:19,450
Fairy Tail's punishment will come later.

208
00:12:21,340 --> 00:12:22,890
Roger...

209
00:12:34,990 --> 00:12:37,060
Nee-chan, that's enough.

210
00:12:37,060 --> 00:12:39,020
I can walk by myself.

211
00:12:39,020 --> 00:12:43,670
I wasn't able to do anything, 
so this is the least I can do.

212
00:12:43,670 --> 00:12:44,900
Nee-chan...

213
00:12:49,060 --> 00:12:52,140
Don't you even understand the basics?

214
00:12:52,140 --> 00:12:53,420
What?

215
00:12:53,420 --> 00:12:58,290
No matter how powerful your spells are, if 
they don't hit your opponent, they're worthless.

216
00:12:58,560 --> 00:12:59,880
Card Magic!

217
00:13:00,130 --> 00:13:02,930
Heaven! Reverse Death! Mountain!

218
00:13:02,930 --> 00:13:04,170
Summoned Lightning!

219
00:13:06,340 --> 00:13:08,480
Écriture of Darkness.

220
00:13:09,140 --> 00:13:10,300
Rejection!

221
00:13:14,890 --> 00:13:16,170
What's that?

222
00:13:16,170 --> 00:13:18,630
That's... Cana!

223
00:13:20,910 --> 00:13:22,210
You're a stubborn one.

224
00:13:22,210 --> 00:13:25,030
Definitely one of the guild's old guard.

225
00:13:25,850 --> 00:13:27,320
Take it back!

226
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:31,300
Take back what you said about 
Juvia being Phantom's woman!

227
00:13:35,610 --> 00:13:36,600
Cana!

228
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:39,080
Damn it, what the hell is going on?

229
00:13:41,300 --> 00:13:42,830
Stop it, Freed!

230
00:13:42,830 --> 00:13:44,070
Why, you...

231
00:13:44,070 --> 00:13:45,550
Elfman!

232
00:13:45,550 --> 00:13:47,870
You lost to Eve.

233
00:13:47,870 --> 00:13:49,970
You have no right to join back in the game.

234
00:13:49,970 --> 00:13:51,200
Shut up!

235
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:52,600
That's enough!

236
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:54,270
Aren't we on the same team?

237
00:13:54,890 --> 00:13:57,320
We once were, yes.

238
00:13:57,320 --> 00:14:00,530
But those relationships no
longer apply during this game

239
00:14:00,530 --> 00:14:02,850
since our purpose is to change the guild.

240
00:14:03,770 --> 00:14:05,940
Here, Laxus's enemy is my enemy.

241
00:14:05,940 --> 00:14:08,470
Enough talking!

242
00:14:12,090 --> 00:14:13,780
What's this?

243
00:14:14,290 --> 00:14:18,350
It is forbidden for someone who has 
lost already to re-enter this game.

244
00:14:18,350 --> 00:14:22,710
Those who break the rules will 
receive torture worse than death.

245
00:14:23,110 --> 00:14:24,760
Écriture of Darkness.

246
00:14:24,760 --> 00:14:25,770
Pain.

247
00:14:25,770 --> 00:14:29,190
Those letters will become your reality... 
Will become your every sensation...

248
00:14:33,780 --> 00:14:35,180
Elfman!

249
00:14:35,630 --> 00:14:37,210
Stop this, Freed!

250
00:14:37,210 --> 00:14:39,370
Elfman can't fight anymore!

251
00:14:40,670 --> 00:14:42,270
Écriture of Darkness.

252
00:14:42,270 --> 00:14:43,400
Fear!

253
00:14:43,400 --> 00:14:44,570
Suffering!

254
00:14:51,020 --> 00:14:51,990
Please!

255
00:14:53,140 --> 00:14:54,760
I'll do anything!

256
00:14:55,160 --> 00:14:56,980
Just, save him!

257
00:14:56,980 --> 00:14:58,750
Pain! Pain! Pain!

258
00:14:58,750 --> 00:15:00,740
Pain! Pain! Pain!

259
00:15:02,880 --> 00:15:06,550
No!!

260
00:15:07,980 --> 00:15:09,420
Écriture of Darkness.

261
00:15:10,290 --> 00:15:11,220
Annihilation!

262
00:15:18,100 --> 00:15:19,310
Death?

263
00:15:27,040 --> 00:15:30,320
Let's go home, Elf-niichan!

264
00:15:31,530 --> 00:15:33,160
Lisanna!

265
00:15:38,210 --> 00:15:41,620
Oh... This is odd...

266
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:45,990
I can't move... my body...

267
00:15:45,990 --> 00:15:47,250
Don't speak!

268
00:15:48,150 --> 00:15:50,770
Mira-nee... Where are you?

269
00:15:51,230 --> 00:15:52,490
Right here.

270
00:15:54,610 --> 00:15:56,390
Mira... nee...

271
00:15:56,920 --> 00:15:58,390
You know...

272
00:15:58,980 --> 00:16:00,380
I really...

273
00:16:00,380 --> 00:16:01,100
See...

274
00:16:02,800 --> 00:16:03,920
Lisanna...

275
00:16:05,210 --> 00:16:06,270
Lisanna!

276
00:16:07,350 --> 00:16:09,000
Lisanna!

277
00:16:14,150 --> 00:16:16,490
What is this magical power?

278
00:16:17,070 --> 00:16:18,190
Mirajane...

279
00:16:51,970 --> 00:16:53,070
Écriture of Darkness.

280
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:54,330
Wings!

281
00:17:17,410 --> 00:17:18,510
Begone.

282
00:17:19,040 --> 00:17:22,400
So this is the Take Over 
of the Demon Mirajane?

283
00:17:22,600 --> 00:17:24,450
Satan Soul!

284
00:17:27,340 --> 00:17:29,310
Darkness Stream!

285
00:17:30,640 --> 00:17:31,650
Écriture of...

286
00:17:40,770 --> 00:17:42,410
I have no choice but to use 
the forbidden technique...

287
00:17:42,660 --> 00:17:44,600
You need a demon to beat a demon!

288
00:17:44,600 --> 00:17:46,080
Écriture of Darkness!

289
00:17:47,260 --> 00:17:48,550
Darkness!

290
00:18:14,350 --> 00:18:16,190
Evil Spark!

291
00:18:20,970 --> 00:18:23,650
W-What incredible magical power...

292
00:18:23,650 --> 00:18:25,690
I had heard the rumors, but...

293
00:18:26,010 --> 00:18:30,060
Is this really the same Mirajane?

294
00:18:31,270 --> 00:18:35,060
But I cannot lose!

295
00:18:37,450 --> 00:18:39,410
Darkness Breath!

296
00:18:43,390 --> 00:18:45,010
Darkness Flare Bomb!

297
00:18:48,250 --> 00:18:49,340
Did I get her?

298
00:18:50,790 --> 00:18:52,810
What's that?

299
00:18:57,030 --> 00:18:59,270
She's enveloping herself in river water?

300
00:19:00,060 --> 00:19:02,100
How much magical power does she have?

301
00:19:03,010 --> 00:19:05,630
Evil Explosion!

302
00:19:12,270 --> 00:19:16,230
Soul Extinction!

303
00:19:36,400 --> 00:19:39,280
Freed!

304
00:19:39,280 --> 00:19:41,240
I-I can't win!

305
00:19:41,240 --> 00:19:43,960
So this is the true power of the demon...

306
00:19:46,660 --> 00:19:48,070
Mira-nee!

307
00:20:15,150 --> 00:20:17,540
W-What are you going to do?

308
00:20:23,820 --> 00:20:26,060
There's no point to this battle.

309
00:20:26,520 --> 00:20:29,010
Arrogance of the victor, Mirajane?

310
00:20:29,370 --> 00:20:31,000
Finish me off.

311
00:20:32,110 --> 00:20:33,880
We're allies.

312
00:20:34,410 --> 00:20:36,290
Members of the same guild.

313
00:20:37,500 --> 00:20:38,990
We smile together.

314
00:20:40,010 --> 00:20:41,420
And have a good time together...

315
00:20:42,450 --> 00:20:44,220
And move forward, together...

316
00:20:44,220 --> 00:20:45,560
Shut up!

317
00:20:45,560 --> 00:20:48,010
My only ally is Laxus!

318
00:20:48,770 --> 00:20:50,330
He's not the only one, right?

319
00:20:51,260 --> 00:20:55,000
You've already realized this, Freed...

320
00:20:55,830 --> 00:21:00,610
Although I don't believe relying on 
one person alone is completely bad...

321
00:21:01,650 --> 00:21:04,930
There are lots of people all around you.

322
00:21:06,320 --> 00:21:09,750
And those people are always 
connected with one another.

323
00:21:12,600 --> 00:21:17,430
See? If you stretch out your 
hand, they're so close...

324
00:21:19,980 --> 00:21:25,910
When people realize that it's lonely 
being alone, they'll become kind.

325
00:21:27,510 --> 00:21:29,680
And you've realized it.

326
00:21:42,880 --> 00:21:47,020
I didn't... want to do this...

327
00:21:48,780 --> 00:21:50,120
We know.

328
00:21:51,340 --> 00:21:55,630
Next year, let's enjoy the 
Harvest Festival together, okay?

329
00:22:01,770 --> 00:22:03,030
Nee-chan...

330
00:22:03,030 --> 00:22:04,780
You just can't beat her...

331
00:22:08,160 --> 00:22:12,100
Freed vs. Mirajane: Both remove themselves from contention.

332
00:22:13,280 --> 00:22:15,310
Battle of Fairy Tail...

333
00:22:16,090 --> 00:22:19,400
Only one left... Laxus!

334
00:22:25,230 --> 00:22:33,690
That time we laughed, saying "we're both like each other,"

335
00:22:35,090 --> 00:22:43,870
we even kindly overlooked the little lies.

336
00:22:44,700 --> 00:22:49,970
If we lose a place to go back to together, I don't care.

337
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:58,720
Because I'll protect that smile.

338
00:22:59,100 --> 00:23:03,160
The meetings and partings numerous as the stars in the sky...

339
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:05,610
All the things I don't want to lose...

340
00:23:05,610 --> 00:23:10,290
Right now I feel like I don't need any of them.

341
00:23:10,290 --> 00:23:15,440
I just want to see you by my side,

342
00:23:15,720 --> 00:23:21,070
all my happiness and sadness.

343
00:23:21,070 --> 00:23:23,550
Let's start from here.

344
00:23:23,550 --> 00:23:26,150
Let's start our tomorrow.

345
00:23:26,150 --> 00:23:30,650
Let's do it like we've just been reborn.

346
00:23:30,650 --> 00:23:36,200
Like flowers blown in a summer wind,

347
00:23:36,200 --> 00:23:44,900
let us bloom brightly in this instant.

348
00:23:56,380 --> 00:23:58,790
Finally, it's the showdown with Laxus!

349
00:23:58,790 --> 00:24:01,000
Yeah! I'm all fired up!

350
00:24:01,000 --> 00:24:03,800
Wouldn't it be better for you 
just to take a nap, Natsu?

351
00:24:03,800 --> 00:24:08,150
It's usually the main character that 
beats the final boss like this.

352
00:24:08,150 --> 00:24:09,250
What're you talkin' about?

353
00:24:09,250 --> 00:24:10,890
Then, who's the main character?

354
00:24:10,890 --> 00:24:12,130
You, Happy?

355
00:24:12,130 --> 00:24:13,990
That may be the case...

356
00:24:13,990 --> 00:24:16,860
Next time: Clash at Kardia Cathedral!

357
00:24:16,860 --> 00:24:18,130
Hold it!

358
00:24:18,130 --> 00:24:19,850
Trying to hog the spotlight, huh?

359
00:24:19,850 --> 00:24:20,600
No fair!

360
00:24:20,600 --> 00:24:24,340
When you consider my star 
power, it's only natural.

361
00:24:24,340 --> 00:24:26,590


